        // Instead, we verify that the method was called by spying and invoking the method reflectively,
        // then verifying the spy called the method by using Mockito's verify on the spy's invocation handler.

        // This helper method will invoke the private method on the spy with the given args,
        // and then verify that it was called exactly once.

